## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The findings are limited to the information provided by the sources accessed, and there may be additional factors influencing behavior that are not covered in this report. Furthermore, cultural influences can vary widely across different contexts and may not be universally applicable.

